OL,6,FWhether you're "keeping it real",
OL,7,Fhaving a "glow-up", or "eating and
OL,8,Fleaving no crumbs" could have a lot to
OL,9,Fdo with how old you are.
OL,11,FThe British Council, an organisation
OL,12,Fwhich promotes and educates on UK
OL,13,Fculture, claims some older expressions
OL,14,Fare falling out of fashion as new ones
OL,15,Frise in popularity - driven largely by
OL,16,Fsocial media and Gen Z.
