OL,6,FThe research, led by computational
OL,7,Flinguistics expert Dr Barbara
OL,8,FMcGillivray and natural language
OL,9,Fprocessing specialist Iacopo Ghinassi,
OL,10,Fanalysed millions of online documents
OL,11,Fto track when expressions emerge and
OL,12,Fhow their use changes
OL,14,FDr McGillivray said: "Analysing the
OL,15,Ffrequency and emergence of idioms,
OL,16,Fproverbs, and phrases, we uncover not
OL,17,Fonly the impact of historical events
OL,18,Fbut also how the digital era shapes
OL,19,Fthe language we use today.
