OL,6,FThe British Council found some idioms
OL,7,Fappeared to skip a generation, with
OL,8,Fphrases like "throw in the towel" and
OL,9,F"joie de vivre" being popular among
OL,10,Folder generations and gen Z, but not
OL,11,Fwith millenials.
OL,13,FThis could show that some idioms are
OL,14,Fbeing revived or reinvented among
OL,15,Fyounger speakers, the British Council
OL,16,Fsaid.
