OL,6,FMark Walker, director of English and
OL,7,Fexams at the British Council, said:
OL,8,F"This latest study into the evolution
OL,9,Fof English explores the phrases we use
OL,10,Fto express shared ideas and
OL,11,Fexperiences ` it shows how much
OL,12,FEnglish is shaped by people around the
OL,13,Fworld and how it continues to grow and
OL,14,Fadapt.
OL,16,F"By celebrating the richness of our
OL,17,Flanguage, we're not just looking at
OL,18,Fits past, but also at the future of
OL,19,FEnglish.
